Package: fgdiag
Architecture: all
Depends: mtools, console-tools, time, less, smartmontools, libtui-ruby (>= 1.9), ruby, lsscsi, dialog, lshw, xresprobe, dmidecode, libopen4-ruby1.8 | fgdiag-open4 (= ${binary:Version}), e2fsprogs (>= 1.41.3), libbytes-ruby1.8 (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: i2c-tools
Description: Free Geek Diagnostics
 Software used to test hardware at Free Geek.

Package: fgdiag-open4
Architecture: all
Depends: ruby1.8
Conflicts: libopen4-ruby1.8
Description: library for managing child processes (Ruby 1.8)
 Repackaged version for use by fgdiag because Debian Etch doesn't have
 it.

Package: libbytes-ruby1.8
Architecture: all
Depends: ruby1.8
Description: library for calculating bytes values (Ruby 1.8)
 This library adds to_bytes, to_hertz, and to_bitspersecond methods to
 the String, Fixnum, and Float class.
 .
 This code is used by fgdb and disktest.
